# Usage of the function
List of multiple directories to be checket
check-partitions.py is checking the list of given direvtories and sends an email
    if threshold is higher then specified with -t NUMBER
if -s options is not provided function will loop every 5 seconds and send email if neccessary
check-partitions.py uses functions specified in check_partition_func.py
python check-partitions.py -s -t 20 -m akif05@gmail.com / /etc /var /home 

